c: 7
v: 164
t: "Bathi abanye abantu phakathi kwabo besakuthi: “Kanjani na ukuba nishumayeze abantu ngoAllâh Asele Eza kubatshabalalisa okanye Abohlwaye ngesohlwayo esibuhlungu? (Abashumayeli bathi): “Senzela ukuba (thina) singabi natyala eNkosini yenu [uAllâh, (kuba)] mhlawumbi baya kumoyika uAllâh.”"